The optional libgmlvideo-ffmpeg.so plugin in lib/ statically links FFmpeg
under LGPL 2.1 or later:

    libavcodec, libavformat, libavutil, libswresample, libswscale

FFmpeg version: n4.4.5 (build options: --disable-everything plus a fixed
set of LGPL-only decoders, demuxers, parsers and protocols; see the
gmloader-next build.txt for the exact configure line).

Full source code for this version is available from the upstream project:

    https://git.ffmpeg.org/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/tag/refs/tags/n4.4.5
    https://ffmpeg.org/releases/ffmpeg-4.4.5.tar.xz

The LGPL 2.1 license text is in FFmpeg.LGPLv2.1 alongside this file.
